<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>823</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>zhǔ yǐ hū zhào zhōng guó 迦南823</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zǒu guò le qiān shān wàn shuǐ, gǎn dòng yuè lái yuè qiáng liè.
 bù qū de ér nǚ qiān qiān wàn wàn, yuàn wèi zhǔ sǎ rè xuè.
 zài kǔ zài nán bù huí tóu. mǎn qiāng rè xuè.
 xiōng huái mín zú xiōng huái guó jiā, xiōng huái quán shì jiè.
 zhǔ yǐ hū zhào zhōng guó, zhōng guó yào zǒu xiàng shì jiè.
 zhǔ yào zhù fú zhōng guó, zhōng guó yào zhù fú shì jiè.
 zhè zhèng shì shén de shí hòu, zhè zhèng shì měi hǎo de shí jié.
 wǒ men de guó jiā yǐ jīng shòu gǎn, yuè lái yuè qiáng liè.</lyrics>
</song>